abstract: All relevant ethical guidelines have been followed; any necessary IRB and/or ethics committee approvals have been obtained and details of the IRB/oversight body are included in the manuscript.
author: Angela Cecilia Pesatori; Basilio Tiso; Emanuele Palomba; Ferruccio Ceriotti; Alessandra Bandera; Antonio Muscatello; Valeria Castelli; Andrea Gori; Davide Mangioni; Luciano Riboldi; Michele Carugno; Giorgio Bozzi; ANDREA LOMBARDI; Dario Consonni; Anna Paola Cantu'
title: Characteristics of 1,573 healthcare workers who underwent nasopharyngeal swab for SARS-CoV-2 in Milano, Lombardy, Italy
